out to be able to do the same thing by the end of the day.&quot;Â  That was how engaging my first day as a software developer was for me.</span></div></div><a href="http://phnompenhlab.instedd.org/2012/07/learning-and-growing-from-my-first.html#more">Read more Â»</a><div class="feedflare">
