<p>This video will teach you how to use the "menu" command and provide options that your users can press in their keypads to navigate your hotline.<br /> <iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/rb7izDxwjaU?feature=player_detailpage" frameborder="0" width="640" height="360"></iframe></p>
<p>I'll try to find time to create a few more videos to showcase the rest of the features (which are plenty!), but hopefully these will get you started.</p>
